# Velocity Product

- Product is **Velocity**, a native IDE — not a VS Code theme/skin.
- Code-OSS under `src/` is reference / feature oracle / compatibility bunker / perf baseline only.
- New work lives in `apps/native-shell` and `packages/*`.
- Feature parity means modular lazy features, not bloat parity.
- No telemetry, surveys, Copilot, or Microsoft marketplace by default.
- Codename is rename-ready; do not hardcode irreversible branding.
- Prioritize a running app and measurable progress.
